  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">UNDSS, through CERF funds aims to increase humanitarian access to areas where lifesaving interventions are required by agencies that are responding. The additional UNDSS presence will develop security awareness, identify security threats, analyze such threats in a timely manner, recommend security measures and procedures, and provide operational security support; all towards supporting effective decision making. 8 Security Risk assessments will be conducted and 40 briefings provided to Security Management Teams.</narrative>
